fields.name: enclave
docs: Represents the state of the quote verifiers enclave.

fields.name: authority
docs: The authority of the EnclaveAccount which is permitted to make account changes.

fields.name: queue
docs: Queue used for attestation to verify a MRENCLAVE measurement.

fields.name: createdAt
docs: The unix timestamp when the quote was created.

fields.name: lastHeartbeat
docs: The last time the quote heartbeated on-chain.

fields.name: gatewayUri
docs: URI location of the verifier's gateway.

fields.name: isOnQueue
docs: Whether the quote is located on the AttestationQueues buffer.

fields.name: finalizedEpoch
docs: The last epoch that has completed. cleared after registered with the
staking program.

fields.name: currentEpoch
docs: The current epoch info being used by the oracle. for stake. Will moved
to finalized_epoch as soon as the epoch is over.

fields.name: ebuf
docs: Reserved.

accounts.name: PullFeedAccountData
docs: A representation of the data in a pull feed account.

fields.name: submissions
docs: The oracle submissions for this feed.

fields.name: authority
docs: The public key of the authority that can update the feed hash that
this account will use for registering updates.

fields.name: queue
docs: The public key of the queue which oracles must be bound to in order to
submit data to this feed.

fields.name: feedHash
docs: SHA-256 hash of the job schema oracles will execute to produce data
for this feed.

fields.name: initializedAt
docs: The slot at which this account was initialized.

accounts.name: QueueAccountData
docs: An Queue represents a round-robin queue of oracle oracles who attest on-chain
whether a Switchboard Function was executed within an enclave against an expected set of
enclave measurements.
For an oracle to join the queue, the oracle must first submit their enclave quote on-chain and
wait for an existing oracle to attest their quote. If the oracle's quote matches an expected
measurement within the queues mr_enclaves config, it is granted permissions and will start
being assigned update requests.

fields.name: authority
docs: The address of the authority which is permitted to add/remove allowed enclave measurements.

fields.name: mrEnclaves
docs: Allowed enclave measurements.

fields.name: oracleKeys
docs: The addresses of the quote oracles who have a valid
verification status and have heartbeated on-chain recently.

fields.name: maxQuoteVerificationAge
docs: The maximum allowable time until a EnclaveAccount needs to be re-verified on-chain.

fields.name: lastHeartbeat
docs: The unix timestamp when the last quote oracle heartbeated on-chain.

fields.name: oracleMinStake
docs: The minimum number of lamports a quote oracle needs to lock-up in order to heartbeat and verify other quotes.

fields.name: mrEnclavesLen
docs: The number of allowed enclave measurements.

fields.name: oracleKeysLen
docs: The length of valid quote oracles for the given attestation queue.

fields.name: reward
docs: The reward paid to quote oracles for attesting on-chain.

fields.name: currIdx
docs: Incrementer used to track the current quote oracle permitted to run any available functions.

fields.name: gcIdx
docs: Incrementer used to garbage collect and remove stale quote oracles.

fields.name: ebuf6
docs: Reserved.

fields.name: value
docs: The median value of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: stdDev
docs: The standard deviation of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: mean
docs: The mean of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: range
docs: The range of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: minValue
docs: The minimum value of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: maxValue
docs: The maximum value of the submissions needed for quorom size

fields.name: numSamples
docs: The number of samples used to calculate this result

fields.name: slot
docs: The slot at which this value was signed.

fields.name: minSlot
docs: The slot at which the first considered submission was made

fields.name: maxSlot
docs: The slot at which the last considered submission was made

fields.name: oracle
docs: The public key of the oracle that submitted this value.

fields.name: slot
docs: The slot at which this value was signed.

fields.name: value
docs: The value that was submitted.

fields.name: enclaveSigner
docs: The address of the signer generated within an enclave.

fields.name: mrEnclave
docs: The quotes MRENCLAVE measurement dictating the contents of the secure enclave.

fields.name: verificationStatus
docs: The VerificationStatus of the quote.

fields.name: verificationTimestamp
docs: The unix timestamp when the quote was last verified.

fields.name: validUntil
docs: The unix timestamp when the quotes verification status expires.

fields.name: quoteRegistry
docs: The off-chain registry where the verifiers quote can be located.

fields.name: registryKey
docs: Key to lookup the buffer data on IPFS or an alternative decentralized storage solution.

fields.name: secp256k1Signer
docs: The secp256k1 public key of the enclave signer. Derived from the enclave_signer.

fields.name: ebuf4
docs: Reserved.
